---
title: Prawn and Tomato Gnocchi with Brazil Nut Pesto
description: Once you’ve seen how easy it is to make a homemade pesto, bursting with fresh herby flavour, you’ll never reach for the shop-bought variety again! Paired with pan-fried crispy gnocchi and deliciously juicy prawns, this 30-minute recipe makes for an easy but impressive dinner.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/prawn-and-tomato-gnocchi-wk43-5830979e.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/prawn-and-tomato-gnocchi-wk43-eebcca9c.pdf
